Introduction

MYTRO is a South Korean pre-debut trot boy group formed in collaboration between SM Entertainment and TV Chosun. Comprising five members—Tey, Jung Yoonjae, Shohei, Lim Chaepyoung, and Seo Woohyeok—MYTRO is set to embark on their journey as a trot idol group. Their television program will air in Korea and Japan in October 2024.
